@SakuyaShirase
There was nothing more to set. They are both aware and they both know they missed the boat. They both regret it a bit, as you can see on p41, but the only thing left is moving on. How does getting a bj and kiss make him move on? Because it kinda drives home that it's real. The faces he makes are basically "that day, a part of me died", so he can either kill himself more or try to cut it off and move on. Man, that p41 kinda delivers the final "it might have been" blow. Appreciated end on a positive note.

I honestly can't even feel sad for MC, because he never actually lost her, he gave up on her. So fucking frustrating.
